#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"BashStyle-NG is not loaded upon Shell start.\n"
"\n"
"Click [Enable] to let the application add a startup\n"
"entry for itself into your ${HOME}/.bashrc\n"
"\n"
"If you click [Cancel] changes done here won't take\n"
"effect. This popup will re-appear every time you\n"
"start the application and when there's no entry in\n"
"your ${HOME}/.bashrc\n"
"\n"
"You can add the entry manually like:\n"
"\n"
"        source /usr/share/bashstyle-ng/rc/bashstyle-rc\n"
"\n"
"assuming /usr was the chosen install prefix. "
msgstr ""
"BashStyle-NG wird beim Shell-Start nicht geladen.\n"
"\n"
"[Anwenden] anklicken, um das Programm einen \n"
"Start-Eintrag in ${HOME}/.bashrc einzutragen.\n"
"\n"
"[Abbrechen] Anklicken um dies zu verhindern.\n"
"Alle im Programm gewählten Einstellungen haben\n"
"dann keinen Effekt. Dieses Fenster erscheint\n"
"immer solange kein Eintrag in ${HOME}/.bashrc\n"
"existiert.\n"
"\n"
"Der Eintrag kann manuell wie folgt angelegt werden:\n"
"\n"
"        source /usr/share/bashstyle-ng/rc/bashstyle-rc\n"
"\n"
"wenn /usr das Installations-Präfix ist. "

